  "A transformation matrix A = [[1, 1], [0, 1]] (shear) is applied to a unit square. What shape results and what is its area?": "变换矩阵A = [[1,1] 、 [0,1] (听觉) 适用于单位方形。 何种形状结果及其区域?",
