  "det(A) = 1. The unit square becomes a parallelogram (since the top edge shifts right), but area = |det(A)| * 1 = 1.": "det(A) = 1. 单位正方形变为平行图(自右上边缘倾斜后),但区域= det(A) * * 1 = 1。",
  "Are the points (1,1), (2,3), and (4,7) collinear? Use the determinant test.": "点(1,1),(2,3)和(4,7)圆线?使用决定因素测试。",
