  "What does 'collinear points' mean geometrically?": "什么是“两极点”意味着几何?",
  "Points in the same quadrant": "同一象体中的点",
  "Points that are equidistant from each other": "彼此相距相等的点",
  "Points that form a triangle": "构成三角形的点",
  "Points that all lie on the same straight line": "所有点都位于同一直线上",
  "Collinear points lie on a single straight line. The determinant test detects this because collinear points form a 'triangle' with zero area.": "连线点位于单一直线上。 决定因素测试检测到这一点, 因为圆线点形成一个带零区域的“ 三角 ” 。",
  "What is a 'rigid transformation' in terms of determinants?": "就决定因素而言,什么是“硬性转变”?",
  "A transformation with det = 0": "det = 0的变换",
  "A transformation that does not move any points": "不移动任何点的转换",
  "A transformation with |det| = 1 that preserves distances and angles": "使用 det= 1 保持距离和角度的转换",
  "Any transformation with positive determinant": "具有积极决定因素的任何转变",
  "Rigid transformations (rotations and reflections) have |det| = 1. They preserve distances, angles, and areas. Rotations have det = +1, reflections have det = -1.": "硬质变换( 旋转和反射) = = 1. 保持距离、 角度和区域。 旋转 = +1, 反射 = - 1 。",
  "What does 'affine transformation' mean?": "\"牛油果变换\"是什么意思?",
  "A transformation that preserves all distances": "保持所有距离的转变",
  "A nonlinear transformation": "非线性变换",
  "A transformation of the form T(x) = Ax + b, combining a linear map with a translation": "T(x) = Ax +b,将线形地图与翻译合并的表单 T(x) = Ax +b的转换",
  "A transformation that only rotates": "仅旋转的转换",
  "An affine transformation combines a linear transformation (matrix multiplication) with a translation. The area scaling factor is still |det(A)|.": "Affine 转换将线性转换( 矩阵乘法) 和 翻译结合起来。 区域缩放系数仍然是 det( A)  。",
  "What is an 'orthogonal matrix'?": "什么是“ 垂直矩阵 ” ?",
  "A matrix whose inverse equals its transpose: A^(-1) = A^T": "A(-1) = AT",
  "A matrix with all entries equal to 0 or 1": "包含所有条目等于 0 或 1 的矩阵表",
  "A rectangular matrix with orthogonal columns": "带有正纵列的矩形矩形矩阵",
  "A diagonal matrix": "对角矩阵",
  "An orthogonal matrix satisfies A^T A = I. Its determinant is +1 or -1. Orthogonal matrices represent rotations (det=+1) and reflections (det=-1).": "矩形矩阵满足 AQT A = I 。 其决定因素是 +1 或 - 1 。 矩形矩阵代表旋转 (det1) 和反射 (det=-1) 。",
  "What is a 'homogeneous coordinate'?": "什么是“相互协调”?",
  "Adding an extra coordinate (usually 1) to represent points, enabling translations as matrix multiplications": "添加额外坐标(通常为1个)以代表点,使翻译成为矩阵乘数",
  "A coordinate that is always zero": "总是为零的坐标坐标",
  "A coordinate system where all points have the same distance from the origin": "坐标系统, 在所有点与源的距离相同 。",
  "A normalized coordinate system": "标准化协调系统",
  "Homogeneous coordinates represent a 2D point (x,y) as (x,y,1). This allows translations to be expressed as matrix multiplications, useful in computer graphics and the determinant-based collinearity test.": "等同坐标表示2D点(x,y)为(x,y,1),这样可以将译文表述为矩阵乘法,用于计算机图形和基于决定因素的共线测试。",
  "What does 'coplanar' mean for four points in 3D?": "3D中四点的“coplanar”是什么意思?",
  "All four points are equidistant": "四点均为等距",
  "The points form a regular tetrahedron": "点构成常规四面体",
  "The points are collinear": "点是圆线",
  "All four points lie in the same plane": "四点都在同一架飞机上",
  "Four points are coplanar if they all lie in a single plane. This can be tested using a 4x4 determinant (with homogeneous coordinates): if det = 0, the points are coplanar.": "四点如果都停留在单平面上,则为共平面共平点。这可以用4x4的决定因素(同位坐标)进行测试:如果 dt = 0,则各点为共平面。",
  "What is the 'Shoelace formula' for polygon area?": "多边形区域的“ hoelace 公式” 是什么 ?",
  "A formula using the cross product in 3D": "3D 中使用交叉产品的公式",
  "A formula using determinants of consecutive vertex pairs to compute the area of a simple polygon": "一种公式,使用连续顶面对数的决定因素来计算一个简单多边形的面积",
  "A method for triangulating a polygon": "多边形三角三角测绘方法",
  "A formula for the perimeter of a polygon": "多边形周边的公式",
  "The Shoelace formula computes polygon area as (1/2)|sum of (x_i * y_{i+1} - x_{i+1} * y_i)|. Each term is a 2x2 determinant formed by consecutive vertices.": "Shoelace 公式将多边形区域计算为 (x_i * yi+1} - xi+1} * y_i) 。 每个术语都是由连续的顶点组成的 2x2 决定因素 。",
  "What is an 'isometry'?": "什么是“测量法”?",
  "A transformation that doubles all areas": "使所有领域翻一番的转型",
  "A distance-preserving transformation (|det| = 1 for the linear part)": "保持距离变换(det=线性部分1)",
  "A transformation with zero determinant": "具有零决定因素的转型",
  "A transformation that changes distances proportionally": "按比例改变距离的转换",
  "An isometry preserves distances. In matrix form, the linear part must be orthogonal with |det| = 1. Examples include rotations, reflections, and translations.": "等离子度保持距离。 在矩阵形式中, 线性部分必须正对齐, 包括旋转、 反射和翻译 。",
  "What is a 'dilation' (uniform scaling) in terms of determinants?": "就决定因素而言,什么是“差异”(统一缩放)?",
  "A rotation by k degrees": "以 k 度旋转",
  "A transformation with det = k": "det=k的变换",
  "A transformation that preserves area": "保留面积的变换",
  "A transformation with matrix kI and det = k^n": "带有矩阵 kI 和 det = kn 的转换",
  "A dilation by factor k in n dimensions has matrix kI and det = k^n. Areas scale by k^2 in 2D, volumes by k^3 in 3D.": "以因子 k 乘以 n 维的比值乘以 k, 矩阵 kI 和 dt = kn。 区域比例为 k2 , 2D , 3D 体积为 k3 。",
  "What does the 'handedness' (chirality) of a transformation refer to?": "转变的“权势”指的是什么?",
  "Whether the transformation preserves (det > 0) or reverses (det < 0) the right-hand rule orientation": "变换是否保留( idt > 0) 或反向( idt < 0) 右手规则方向",
  "The direction of the largest eigenvector": "最大导体方向",
  "Whether the transformation uses the left or right column for computation": "变换是否使用左栏或右栏进行计算",
  "Whether the matrix is upper or lower triangular": "矩阵表是上三角还是下三角",
  "A positive determinant preserves handedness (right-hand stays right-hand). A negative determinant reverses it, like looking in a mirror.": "积极的决定因素保留了手势(右手保持右手 ) 。 消极的决定因素扭转了它,就像照镜子一样。",
  "An architect calculates the area of a quadrilateral roof section with vertices (0,0), (6,0), (7,5), and (1,4) using the Shoelace formula. What is the area?": "建筑师使用休氏公式计算四边屋顶部分的面积(0,0),(6,0),(7,5)和(1,4),并使用休氏公式计算。",
