  "A civil engineer uses the cross product to find the area of a triangular section of land with edge vectors u = [3,0,4] and v = [0,5,0]. The area is (1/2)|u x v|. What is |u x v|?": "土木工程师使用交叉产品在三角地带找到有边缘矢量的 u = [3,0,4] 和 v = [0,5,0] 的面积。该面积是 (1/2) u x v 。 u x v  是什么?",
