  "A GIS analyst computes the area of a triangular region with vertices (10,20), (40,20), and (25,50) in meters. Using the determinant formula, what is the area?": "地理信息系统分析员计算三角区域面积(10,20,40,20,25,50米)。使用决定因素公式计算出三角区域面积(10,20,40,20)和(25,50米)。",
