  "A 3D graphics programmer applies a rotation matrix R (det=1) to a model, then a non-uniform scale S = diag(2,1,3). The original model has volume V. What is the new volume?": "3D 图形程序程序员将旋转矩阵 R (det=1) 应用于模型,然后是非统一比例S = diag (2,1,3) 。 原始模型有卷V。 新音量是什么?",
