  "A landscape architect designs an irregular polygon plot with vertices (0,0), (4,0), (5,3), (2,5), (-1,3). Using the Shoelace formula, what is the area?": "地貌设计师设计一个非常规多边形图,带有顶部(0,0,4,0,5,3,2,5,5,1,3),使用休克拉特公式,面积是多少?",
