  "A satellite imaging specialist transforms coordinates using A = [[0.6, -0.8], [0.8, 0.6]] (a rotation). She applies it to a country with area 500,000 km^2. What is the area in the transformed coordinates?": "A=[0.6,-0.8],[0.8,0.6](旋转])的卫星成像专家变形坐标。她将其应用于一个面积为500,000平方公里的国家。2 变形坐标的面积是多少?",
